每500個小孩就會有1個出現多指畸形。<ref name="drgreene">{{Cite web|author=Khanh-Van Le-Bucklin MD & Rebecca Hicks M.D.|year=2008|url=http://www.drgreene.com/21_182.html|title=Polydactylism FAQ|accessdate=2009-02-09|archive-date=2009-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203072111/http://drgreene.com/21_182.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[非洲|非洲]]裔黑人小孩會較多患上軸後多指畸形，黑人男孩出現軸後多指畸形差不多是白人的10倍。一項研究發現每1000個白人男性中，就有2.3個患上多指畸形，而1000個白人女性中，則有0.6個患上；1000個黑人男性中，有13.5個會患有此病，1000個黑人女性中，則有11.1個患上。<ref name="emedicine">{{Cite web|author=Carter G Abel & Denise M McCarthy|year=2008|url=http://www.emedicine.com/DERM/topic692.htm|title=Supernumerary Digit|accessdate=2009-02-09|archive-date=2008-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080921105734/http://www.emedicine.com/derm/topic692.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

